    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"Society Radar\"\nsubtitle: \"Sentiment across six aspects of public life, by administration\"\n---\n\n\n\nEach line is one presidential administration. Angles are six aspects of\npublic life; the radial distance represents sentiment from **−10** (extreme\nnegative) at the center to **+10** (extreme positive) at the outer edge,\nwith **0** as the baseline at the middle ring. A line passing *through* the\nmiddle ring on an axis means sentiment on that aspect was neutral during\nthat administration.\n\n::: {.callout-important appearance=\"simple\"}\n**These scores are editorial calibrations.** They anchor on measurable\nsignals used elsewhere on this site (UMCSENT, Gallup approval, NBER\nrecessions, wars-in-progress, published violent-crime indices) plus\nhistorical commentary, but the final single-number −10/+10 mapping per\naspect is a single author's aggregation. See [Methodology](about.qmd) for\nthe full caveats, and `data/sentiment/society_scores.csv` in the repo for\nthe rationale attached to each score. Corrections welcome via the repo.\n:::\n\n## Radar {#radar}\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"echarts4r html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-e6059d2f011d0773f754\" style=\"width:100%;height:500px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-e6059d2f011d0773f754\">{\"x\":{\"theme\":\"custom\",\"tl\":false,\"draw\":true,\"renderer\":\"canvas\",\"events\":[],\"buttons\":[],\"opts\":{\"color\":[\"#e63946\",\"#f77f00\",\"#fcbf49\",\"#2f9e44\",\"#2a6f97\",\"#7b2cbf\"],\"radar\":[{\"indicator\":[{\"name\":\"Public Safety\",\"max\":10,\"min\":-10},{\"name\":\"Economy\",\"max\":10,\"min\":-10},{\"name\":\"Health\",\"max\":10,\"min\":-10},{\"name\":\"Prosperity\",\"max\":10,\"min\":-10},{\"name\":\"Happiness\",\"max\":10,\"min\":-10},{\"name\":\"Peace\",\"max\":10,\"min\":-10}],\"radius\":\"68%\",\"shape\":\"polygon\",\"splitNumber\":4,\"name\":{\"textStyle\":{\"fontSize\":13,\"color\":\"#1d3557\",\"fontWeight\":600}},\"axisLine\":{\"lineStyle\":{\"color\":\"#adb5bd\"}},\"splitLine\":{\"lineStyle\":{\"color\":\"#dee2e6\"}},\"splitArea\":{\"show\":true,\"areaStyle\":{\"color\":[\"#ffffff\",\"#f8f9fa\"]}}}],\"series\":[{\"type\":\"radar\",\"data\":[{\"value\":[6,8,4,7,6,3],\"name\":\"Bill Clinton\"},{\"value\":[-3,-2,1,-3,-3,-7],\"name\":\"George W. Bush\"},{\"value\":[2,3,4,1,2,-1],\"name\":\"Barack Obama\"},{\"value\":[-2,1,-8,0,-4,2],\"name\":\"Donald Trump (1st term)\"},{\"value\":[-2,-3,-1,-4,-5,-5],\"name\":\"Joe Biden\"},{\"value\":[-1,-2,0,-3,-6,-3],\"name\":\"Donald Trump (2nd term)\"}],\"radarIndex\":0,\"min\":-10,\"symbol\":\"circle\",\"symbolSize\":6,\"lineStyle\":{\"width\":2},\"areaStyle\":{\"opacity\":0.18}}],\"legend\":{\"data\":[\"Bill Clinton\",\"George W. Bush\",\"Barack Obama\",\"Donald Trump (1st term)\",\"Joe Biden\",\"Donald Trump (2nd term)\"],\"show\":true,\"type\":\"plain\",\"top\":0,\"textStyle\":{\"fontSize\":11}},\"tooltip\":{\"trigger\":\"item\",\"formatter\":\"\\n              function(p){\\n                var aspects = [\\\"Public Safety\\\",\\\"Economy\\\",\\\"Health\\\",\\\"Prosperity\\\",\\\"Happiness\\\",\\\"Peace\\\"];\\n                var v = p.value;\\n                return '<b>' + p.name + '<\\/b><br/>' +\\n                  aspects.map(function(a,i){\\n                    var val = v[i];\\n                    if (typeof val !== 'number' || !isFinite(val)) return a + ': —';\\n                    var sign = val > 0 ? '+' : '';\\n                    return a + ': ' + sign + val;\\n                  }).join('<br/>');\\n              }\"},\"title\":[{\"left\":\"center\",\"text\":\"Sentiment across six aspects of society, by administration\",\"subtext\":\"−10 extreme negative · 0 baseline (middle ring) · +10 extreme positive\"}]},\"dispose\":true,\"theme2\":true,\"customTheme\":\"{\\n  \\\"color\\\": [\\\"#2a6f97\\\",\\\"#e07a5f\\\",\\\"#bc4749\\\",\\\"#6a4c93\\\",\\\"#2f9e44\\\",\\\"#f2c14e\\\",\\\"#1d3557\\\",\\\"#6c757d\\\"],\\n  \\\"backgroundColor\\\": \\\"transparent\\\",\\n  \\\"textStyle\\\": { \\\"fontFamily\\\": \\\"system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif\\\" },\\n  \\\"title\\\": {\\n    \\\"top\\\": 8,\\n    \\\"padding\\\": [6, 10, 14, 10],\\n    \\\"textStyle\\\": { \\\"fontWeight\\\": \\\"600\\\", \\\"fontSize\\\": 16 },\\n    \\\"subtextStyle\\\": { \\\"fontSize\\\": 12, \\\"color\\\": \\\"#6c757d\\\" }\\n  },\\n  \\\"legend\\\": {\\n    \\\"top\\\": 56,\\n    \\\"padding\\\": [4, 10, 4, 10],\\n    \\\"textStyle\\\": { \\\"color\\\": \\\"#495057\\\" }\\n  },\\n  \\\"grid\\\": { \\\"containLabel\\\": true, \\\"left\\\": 48, \\\"right\\\": 24, \\\"top\\\": 95, \\\"bottom\\\": 40 },\\n  \\\"xAxis\\\": { \\\"axisLine\\\": { \\\"lineStyle\\\": { \\\"color\\\": \\\"#adb5bd\\\" } } },\\n  \\\"yAxis\\\": { \\\"splitLine\\\": { \\\"lineStyle\\\": { \\\"color\\\": \\\"#e9ecef\\\" } } }\\n}\",\"theme_name\":\"econ\"},\"evals\":[\"opts.tooltip.formatter\"],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n## Scores table {#table}\n\nFull list of curated scores, with per-row justification notes. Edit\n`data/sentiment/society_scores.csv` to refine.\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"reactable html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-8569bc6068dec97a5917\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-8569bc6068dec97a5917\">{\"x\":{\"tag\":{\"name\":\"Reactable\",\"attribs\":{\"data\":{\"president\":[\"Bill Clinton\",\"Bill Clinton\",\"Bill Clinton\",\"Bill Clinton\",\"Bill Clinton\",\"Bill Clinton\",\"George W. Bush\",\"George W. Bush\",\"George W. Bush\",\"George W. Bush\",\"George W. Bush\",\"George W. Bush\",\"Barack Obama\",\"Barack Obama\",\"Barack Obama\",\"Barack Obama\",\"Barack Obama\",\"Barack Obama\",\"Donald Trump (1st term)\",\"Donald Trump (1st term)\",\"Donald Trump (1st term)\",\"Donald Trump (1st term)\",\"Donald Trump (1st term)\",\"Dona