Recession starts late 2007; ended in collapse.\",\"Stable life-expectancy; Medicare Part D enacted (+); no major pandemic.\",\"Housing bubble and crash; wage stagnation in middle class; net job loss by end.\",\"Post-9/11 anxiety; war fatigue; UMCSENT dropped from 90s to 60s by exit.\",\"Two major wars launched (Afghanistan 2001, Iraq 2003); both active through term.\",\"Crime decline continued; Boston Marathon bombing and Sandy Hook were shocks.\",\"Slow but steady recovery from GFC; unemployment 10% to 4.7% over term.\",\"Affordable Care Act expanded coverage to 20M+ Americans; life expectancy slight decline late term.\",\"Recovery uneven — top earners recovered fastest; median income recovered by 2015.\",\"Mood recovered from GFC lows; moderate UMCSENT (~80s).\",\"Iraq drawdown but Libya, Syria, ISIS emergence; drone program expanded.\",\"Violent-crime uptick in 2020 (COVID/protests); overall mixed.\",\"Strong pre-COVID expansion then sharp COVID collapse + rapid rebound.\",\"COVID-19: 400K+ US deaths during term; Operation Warp Speed (+); CDC strain.\",\"Strong wage growth pre-COVID; massive pandemic disruption in Q2-Q4 2020.\",\"Polarization intensified; COVID isolation; UMCSENT slid from 100 to 70s.\",\"No new wars started; Abraham Accords; Afghanistan withdrawal negotiated.\",\"Violent-crime concerns persisted in polling though measured rates fell 2022-24.\",\"Highest inflation in 40 years (9% peak); aggressive Fed tightening; mild labor softening.\",\"COVID recovery but healthcare inflation; drug-pricing reform (+); life expectancy partial recovery.\",\"Real-wage compression from inflation early; partial recovery late term; housing unaffordable.\",\"UMCSENT at historic lows (~50s); polarization; inflation-driven cost-of-living strain.\",\"Russia invasion of Ukraine; chaotic Afghanistan withdrawal; Hamas attack + Gaza war.\",\"Early term; reported violent-crime rates mixed; immigration-enforcement controversies.\",\"Tariff-driven uncertainty; market volatility; Q1 2026 growth print weak.\",\"No major public-health shock to date; partial measure.\",\"Tariff cost passed to consumers; real incomes pressured; investment uncertainty.\",\"UMCSENT below 60 — multi-year lows; consumer expectations index at recession levels.\",\"Ukraine and Middle East conflicts continuing; NATO tensions; trade-war rhetoric.\"]},\"columns\":[{\"id\":\"president\",\"name\":\"President\",\"type\":\"character\",\"minWidth\":180},{\"id\":\"party\",\"name\":\"Party\",\"type\":\"character\",\"aggregate\":\"unique\",\"cell\":[{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.7rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#2a6f97\"}},\"children\":[\"DEMOCRATIC\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.7rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#2a6f97\"}},\"children\":[\"DEMOCRATIC\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.7rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#2a6f97\"}},\"children\":[\"DEMOCRATIC\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.7rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#2a6f97\"}},\"children\":[\"DEMOCRATIC\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.7rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":\"#2a6f97\"}},\"children\":[\"DEMOCRATIC\"]},{\"name\":\"span\",\"attribs\":{\"style\":{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"padding\":\"2px 8px\",\"border-radius\":\"3px\",\"font-size\":\"0.7rem\",\"font-weight\":\"600\",\"color\":\"#fff\",\"background\":